[Our heartfelt thanks to Sabine and Susan for their hard work in
finding and obtaining a translation of the original report. We look
forward to seeing the results of the confirmatory examinations and for
any related commentaries by our readers in Tehran.

While Iran was once in sight of this disease being truly sporadic,
latterly, outbreaks have been reported throughout the country.

The HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Iran is available at
http://healthmap.org/r/00Hj. - Mod.MHJ]
